{"tid":951724,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人訓得多會頭痛?","createTime":"2018-12-22T14:38:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-22T20:15:00.000Z","uid":123991,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a18eb9964a00fcccc2d35c0b65ca6096a961ffcb","tid":951724,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T14:38:25.000Z","msg":"如題, 萬試萬靈 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平時訓開5個鐘, 尋晚太攰唔記得較鬧鐘一訓又訓咗9個鐘, 跟住又頭痛<br />\n個人係精神但keep住個頭有少少痛咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1f8effd65c9b9830296362a317007f24dab6928","tid":951724,"uid":107364,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T14:39:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7aa6e1e4382d181ebaaed8fb21d28551f88961e6","tid":951724,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1f8effd65c9b9830296362a317007f24dab6928","tid":951724,"uid":107364,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T14:39:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T14:46:17.000Z","msg":"以前我都以為我唔得, 都係早一年前練返黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfa389fee8d9416cd038435ba50f2516d4700d7b","tid":951724,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T14:47:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"41da602dfa0eaef8bdb70ace608b491ddb85abba","tid":951724,"uid":34147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T14:53:54.000Z","msg":"但你瞓到九個鐘而無自然醒，證明你係有呢個需要瞓返多啲。而家瞓得少後生仲捱到，老咗要還㗎。"},{"pid":"8643248bf0e9bb396833041895f14f3d257e1865","tid":951724,"uid":223084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T15:24:39.000Z","msg":"失眠和頭痛都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aee663e0145144b9150beb3734b30bbef7f3e34d","tid":951724,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cfa389fee8d9416cd038435ba50f2516d4700d7b","tid":951724,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7aa6e1e4382d181ebaaed8fb21d28551f88961e6","tid":951724,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1f8effd65c9b9830296362a317007f24dab6928","tid":951724,"uid":107364,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T14:39:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T14:46:17.000Z","msg":"以前我都以為我唔得, 都係早一年前練返黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T14:47:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T15:27:02.000Z","msg":"其實你上網 search 下 &quot;how to sleep less but have more energy&quot;, &quot;少睡 &quot;呢d keywords 都好多野睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做唔做就自己決定啦, 例如我上網如果調理埋飲食的話, 訓 4個鐘都得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過呢樣我冇做到, 食野好緊要 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n少少心得分享下, 首先我覺得最重要喺係作息定時, 唔好平時要返工就早訓, 一到星期六日就天光先訓第二朝下午先起身<br />\n<br />\n訓教黎講, 正常一個 sleeping cycle 為4 小時, 每個 cycle 入面有唔同的 stage<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vbLGHQf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvbLGHQf.jpg&h=1d666e7e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wOkrTXW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwOkrTXW.png&h=e464fd6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好問d 圖點睇, 其實d 圖我都 9 upload 嘅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為我都唔明得哂, 最好上網自己補完d 資訊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係大概嘅意思係訓教會有 deep sleep 同 light sleep, 顧名思義 deep sleep 就係先真正為你身體叉電嘅狀態, light sleep 就比較客易醒, 訓得唔淨層<br />\n<br />\n通常每一個 sleeping cycle 完結後都係 light sleep 黎 (以我理論黎講好似係, 真係有興趣就上網 search 下了解多d 唔好信哂我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ), 而中間嘅部份就係 deep sleep. <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>即是你要將 deep sleep 嘅時間增加, light sleep 嘅時間變短</strong></span><br />\n打個比如: 訓四個鐘, 頭半個鐘係 light sleep, 之後果3 個鐘都係 deep sleep, 然後最後半個鐘係 light sleep.<br />\n<br />\n問題黎啦, 你點樣可以增加 deep sleep 嘅時間呢?<br />\n小技巧有好多, 例如：<br />\n- 一開始講嘅調理飲食<br />\n- 臨訓前唔好望 mon 嘅發光物體<br />\n- 放支筆同記事本喺床邊, 如果訓左落床後突然醒起d 野即刻 mark 低, 咁就訓得安心唔洗驚第二朝唔記得<br />\n- 熄 wifi (如果唔係有 msg 黎你又心思思想睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n- 唔好側身同縮埋個人訓, 盡量打平打直個人訓 (好似訓官材咁訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />), 因為側左邊身會壓住心, 側右邊身會壓住唔記得邊度, 打平訓就平均受力<br />\n<br />\n第二, 你點樣可以利用 light sleep 時間呢?<br />\n- 就係喺 light sleep 時間起身 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果每4個鐘一個 cycle 的話, 你一係訓 4, 8, 12 個鐘, 千奇唔好喺 cycle 之中起身, 因為你個人會係喺 deep sleep 模式, 會攰到仆街  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大概你跟住呢d 試下做下, 睇係邊d 方法啱你慢慢就練到<br />\n仲有好多人一日淨係訓一次教 (Biphasic sleep), 咁訓多次教 (polyphasic ) 又點呢? 呢個都可以上網睇下, 好似d 軍人咁, 佢地唔可能每日都訓5個鐘, 所以佢地多數都會用多階段睡眠法<br />\n<br />\n仲有 sleep cycling 雖然話 4 個鐘為一個, 但由 awaking 進入 light sleep 嘅時間未計, 所以如果你真係計 cycle 的話要計埋呢d 時間等等... <br />\n講住咁多先, 有興趣真係上網睇下啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4b89bdda25b85fa75b4ecad996ee10c45270808","tid":951724,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T15:31:42.000Z","msg":"屌，我發覺打錯咗好多字，不過應該仲睇得明 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fb6ac476859f159485541517e9217cd180abd4b","tid":951724,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8643248bf0e9bb396833041895f14f3d257e1865","tid":951724,"uid":223084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T15:24:39.000Z","msg":"失眠和頭痛都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T15:36:05.000Z","msg":"失眠想了解多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日唔洗瞓好似好正咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgm